I'm cutting down the complexity of this project drastically.

The plan is now to simply replace my current PHP-based blogging tool with
something written in Python. As with the existing tool, the new one will use
PostgreSQL as a backing store, though switching to SQLite would be acceptable
if I could do so safely.

/ <- Root
/<YYYY>-<MM> <- Month
/<N+> <- Entry
/;add <- Add entry
/;feed <- Atom feed
/<N+>;edit <- Edit entry

Feed ID: tag:talideon.com,2001:weblog
Feed entry ID: tag:talideon.com,2001:weblog:N+
